<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../includes/head') %>

<body>
  <script>
    var consent=0;
    $(document).ready(function() {
      $('#consent').scroll(function () {
        if(scrollToEnd() && consent===1){
          showContent('#next-btn')
        }else{ // If not visible
          hideContent('#next-btn')
        }
      });
    });
    function updateConsent(i){
      consent=i;
      if(consent===1){
        showContent('#next-btn')
      }else{ // If not visible
        hideContent('#next-btn')
      }
    }
  </script>
  <div class="container">
    <br/>
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <b>Disclaimer/Disclosure</b>
        <br/>
        (Scroll to continue):
      </p>
      <div id="consent" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; overflow-y: scroll;">
        <p style="font-size: 15px;">

          The contents shown in this application are solely based on the personal opinions and ideas of the developers. This application is not-for-profit. There is no conflict of interest between the developers of this application. Users who intend to use this application should always consult his/her physicians or other healthcare providers before starting any exercise program, if necessary. Users understand that there is a risk of injury associated with participating and using this application's exercise programs. Users assume full responsibility for any injuries, losses, and damages that he/she might incur while exercising or using the exercise programs generated by this application. Users waive all claims against the developers of this application for any and all injuries, claims, or damages that he/she might incur.
          <br/>
          <br/>


          <input type="radio" name="consent" value="1" required onclick="updateConsent(1)"> I have read and understood the above statements by the developers. &nbsp;&nbsp;
          <br/>
          <br/>
          <input type="radio" name="consent" value="0" onclick="updateConsent(0)"> I have not read nor understood the above statements by the developers. &nbsp;&nbsp;


        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="next-btn" style="padding:50px; text-align: center; display: none; "><a type="button" href="/instruction" class="btn btn-success">Next</a></div>
    </div>
    <%- include('../includes/footer') %>
  </div>
</body>

</html>